reviewText: I looked for this movie for years...I watched it all the time when I was a little girl :)
I never received the item but I did get my refund immediately once I reported that I did not get my item.
I bought this because it was a favorite when I was little...and I never forgot about it!  Just a wonderful story!
I had a VHS tape of this from when I was young and I wore it out!  I was so happy to get another one and watch it again.  It's a great cartoon.  Highly recommended.
